disclaimer:

for educational purposes only. not intended to poll coindesk uncontrollably; needs to be updated to use coindesk api instead of web scraping the data.

relevant scripts include:

timer.py #gets Bitcoin price from coindesk every minute for 600 minutes

crypto-tracker.py #args 'coin name' (e.g. 'bitcoin' or 'ethereum') '%d' (e.g. '600' -num of minutes to poll) example: crypto-tracker.py bitcoin 600

crypto-tracker-setup.py #installs necessary python modules currently under development

all the other scripts are for reference and may be incomplete or incorrect
